<paragraph blockId="57.[136,1452,1854,1984]" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">Thallus corticolus, ramificatione subdichotomo. Rami generaliter cavi sed saepe in parte compressi, subtus perforati, perforationibus coalescentibus. Soralia nulla. Apothecia terminalia. Sporae ellipsoideae. Acida usnicum, homosekikaicum, sekikaicum, boninicum, succinprotocetraricum, protocetraricum et fumarprotocetraricum continens</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
